\" /><br />\n<br />\n圍師必缺，你唔使塞死，已經塞死。</span>"},{"pid":"283b9311c2bb0ce7b7ce67a6fa9bdda83fe3d759","tid":1463304,"uid":280349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:46:15.000Z","msg":"放燃燒彈燒傷警察，應唔應該自首？<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dDvLuS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dDvLuS</a>"},{"pid":"6fe918b571b46df1240391634c87978e41b4e409","tid":1463304,"uid":37396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:46:36.000Z","msg":"喂而家唔係和你飛呀<br />\n果個喺上個星期六日已經完咗啦<br />\n而家係做緊癱瘓機場呀"},{"pid":"db158e37140a0ea47227b6eae74339c7b7056310","tid":1463304,"uid":131522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9d7c9d3d17f3643c1154cc5c85be1d039c31566a","tid":1463304,"uid":68471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:45:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">塞旅客一定要塞如果唔係出機場做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n塞嘅話，留返一個counter出黎，放一條極細既路出黎，由佢地排條好長既隊，排都排一兩粒鐘。其他路block Q曬，咁你就人道了無位比人入了。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n圍師必缺，你唔使塞死，已經塞死。</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:50:17.000Z","msg":"就好似之前塞紅隧咁<br />\n留番一條路通車"},{"pid":"3b6a414331f42fa8fadfcc91ab2fe2a01a10a3da","tid":1463304,"uid":300577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:55:21.000Z","msg":"癱瘓香港機場都係目的之一<br />\n癱瘓經濟迫政府表態"}]}